{
  "stem": "11744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the only way we could have been found was if the Germans start to go with a-- with a plane, and they discovered a few of our-- our stronghold like this because they did from up there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They could never have found us otherwise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was never anything organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You got into something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If my husband had two or three friends who said, why don't we blow up that factory, or why don't we sabotage this factory, so they would start to work at sabotaging a factory.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would get a few people from the factory to-- to help them to come their way, and they will be doing sabotage.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, everything was hit and miss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everything we did was hit and miss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had so many organizations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had-- the most forceful one was the communist, because the communists were much better organized than anybody else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were trained for guerrilla warfare, so that they were better organized than we ever were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we fought practically against them, just like we fought against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, it was pathetic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And de Gaulle named them AS-- Armee Secrete.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was really one-- one overall entity of all the resistance under one leadership-- no more the communists, no more the socialists, no more this, no more that-- one army.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right, so that we were trying to work together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't that easy, because at Liberation, for instance, the one who was called the FGP, they were the [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were the communists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they came out with a red flag.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, they went through Paris with a red flag in a car.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, we-- we didn't kill that, I mean.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
